Source: guimup
Section: sound
Priority: optional
Maintainer: Ronald van Engelen <rvengelen@hethooghuis.nl>
Build-Depends: debhelper (>= 8.0.0), autotools-dev, pkg-config, libpcre3, libmpdclient-dev (>= 2.3), libsoup2.4-dev (>= 2.34), libgtkmm-3.0-dev (>= 3.2)
Standards-Version: 3.9.2
Homepage: http://coonsden.com/
Vcs-Git: git://github.com/ronalde/guimup.git
Vcs-Browser: https://github.com/ronalde/guimup.git

Package: guimup
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, libmpdclient2 (>= 2.3), libsoup2.4-1 (>= 2.34), libgtkmm-3.0-1 (>= 3.2)
Enhances: mpd
Provides: mpd-client
Suggests: mpd
Description: Gtk3 Client for MPD (the Music Player Daemon).
 Features include:
  * Support for (locally stored) albumart.
  * Support for audio streams (url).
  * Drag & drop playlist management.
  * Library browser (artist, album, genre, folder, year & timestamp mode.)
  * Database search (artist, album, genre & title mode).
  * Quick search-and-select in the playlist.
  * Mini-mode interface for basic control only.
  * Open folder in external programs to edit tags etc.
  * Generally a light, quick and clean application.

